### Herodotus Book 3: Thaleia \[130\]

|                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |     |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    